This folder contains auto-generated files produced by `./radaptor.sh install` and
`./radaptor.sh build:all`.

Most generated files remain tracked. The path-sensitive runtime maps below are
gitignored and regenerated locally:

- `__autoload__.php`
- `__package_assets__.json`
- `__templates__.php`
- `__themed_templates__.php`

Tracked exceptions that intentionally stay in Git include:

- `.what_is_this`
- `__db_schema_data__.php`
